posting_body: ['VIEW OUR WEBSITE:', '<URL>', 'M Street, managed by Holland Residential', '910 8th Avenue', 'Seattle, WA 98104', 'show contact info', 'Located in the heart of Seattle, M Street apartments are within walking distance to some of the hottest night spots, restaurants and entertainment near First Hill and Seattle University.', 'Come by for a private tour.', 'Copy and Paste this link to view our screening criteria:', '<URL>', 'Huge one bedroom with spacious den, beautifully open living room with a full wall of windows!', 'This huge bedroom can fit a king size bed and your walk in closet will fulfil all your storage needs!', 'This apartment requires a $425 deposit.', 'Community Features', '* Community Lounge', '* Bike Racks', '* Garage Parking', '* Fitness Studio', '* Renters Insurance is Required', '* We are a social community!', 'Find our Yelp, Facebook or Twitter page online.', '* Outdoor Grill Area', '* Resource Center', '* Rooftop Terraces with Amazing Views', '* WiFi Access', '* TV Lounge', '* Easy Access to Public Transportation', '* Controlled Access Parking', '* Extra Storage', '*', "Our prices can change daily, price listed is based on today's availability.", 'Call for details.', '* Professionally Managed', '* Controlled Access', '* Package Acceptance', '* Elevator', '* Reserved Parking', '* Bark Park', '* After-Hours Emergency Maintenance', '* Minutes from Restaurants, Shopping, and Much More', '* Easy Freeway Access', '* E-Lounge', '[#9341315]']
